title: The Gunfighters (Time-Life, The Old West Series).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 1977 Time-Life / 238 pages / 31.3 MB

The book is exactly what I had anticipated it to be, amazing. Even though it wasn't for me but a small NYE's gift, I knew the person receiving it would LOVE it, and they did.

The cover looks like leather and the pages following look like parchment. It is full of both written facts and wonderful western illustrations ( i.e 17th C. posters and ads) and photographs.

If you have someone or you yourself are infatuated with the stories of Wyatt Earp and Jesse James, and fancy yourself an ol' time gun slinger, then this book is right for you
